de.oth.blocklib.world

Enum BlockType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<BlockType>
      • de.oth.blocklib.world.BlockType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BlockType>

    public enum BlockType
extends java.lang.Enum<BlockType>
    Representation of the type of a block in a world array. If a block is added, textures, world and worldmesh needs a reconfiguration.
    See Also:
    WorldMesh, World, TexturedModel
